net.trajano.doxdb

Class DoxID

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.trajano.doxdb.DoxID
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class DoxID
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    An generated ID object. Unlike a UUID, it has less character restrictions. It is a 32 character random number string. Implementation wise it uses a less secure but more performant ThreadLocalRandom generator to generate new values.
    See Also:
